roles.name: Ranger
roles.description: The Ranger is a excellent sniper. They possess a unique skill SNIPER which can penetrate multiple enemies.

roles.name: Warrior
roles.description: The Warrior is a tank. They possess a unique skill TAUNT which increase defenses and aggro enemies.

roles.name: Priest
roles.description: The Priest is a healer. They possess a unique skill HEAL which places an area healing zone.

roles.name: Rogue
roles.description: The Rogue is fast. They possess a unique skill DASH which slashes through enemies dealing massive damage.

roles.name: Wizard
roles.description: The Wizard is slow. They possess a unique skill BLAST which shoots a massive fireball.

roles.name: Berserker
roles.description: The Berserker is mad. They possess a unique skill BERSERK which increases defenses, movement speed and attack speed.

abilities.description: The warrior unleashes a shockwave that taunts and slows enemies
